text: Motey-sur-Saône is a former commune. It is in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in the Haute-Saône department in east France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune of Seveux-Motey.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018 == References == Category:Former communes in Haute-Saône
title: Motey-sur-Saône
